data.description: INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY!! The bones are good on this home with foundation and roof being in perfect shape! All this home needs is some flooring, updating, and some TLC and she is ready to go. This is a perfect home to fix up and keep yourself, flip or turn into a rental. Large lot over an acre with beautiful fenced in backyard and covered back porch. Wonderful flow from entry way to living room that features a fireplace, kitchen and breakfast nook. Formal dining room is great to keep as dining or turn into a play room, game room or flex space. 3 bedrooms on left side of home with jack and Jill bathroom. Primary bedroom on right side of home features two walk in closets, en suite bathroom, tub, shower and more! 2 car garage is ready to store anything you may want.
